Did you come out alone to play?

574
00:36:43,810 --> 00:36:45,070
Hi, sir.

575
00:36:45,810 --> 00:36:46,680
I wasn't out to play.

576
00:36:46,700 --> 00:36:48,590
I plan to go buy
some sweet glutinous rice balls.

577
00:36:49,020 --> 00:36:50,720
My dad used

578
00:36:50,730 --> 00:36:53,280
to buy them to make Mom happy.

579
00:36:56,940 --> 00:36:58,840
How about I take you for some dessert?

580
00:36:59,170 --> 00:36:59,840
Come.

581
00:37:00,060 --> 00:37:00,800
Let's go.

582
00:37:04,100 --> 00:37:04,910
Is it nice?

583
00:37:04,940 --> 00:37:05,649
This is your order.

584
00:37:05,650 --> 00:37:06,579
Okay, thanks.

585
00:37:06,580 --> 00:37:07,420
How's yours, sweetie?

586
00:37:08,130 --> 00:37:10,160
