589
00:37:14,940 --> 00:37:15,990
Sure, wait for a while.

590
00:37:16,330 --> 00:37:17,280
Enjoy them slowly.

591
00:37:18,810 --> 00:37:19,550
Thank you.

592
00:37:19,810 --> 00:37:20,590
No problem.

593
00:37:23,610 --> 00:37:26,030
I'm giving you my pager number.

594
00:37:28,210 --> 00:37:30,160
If you and your mommy need any help,

595
00:37:30,940 --> 00:37:32,510
contact me through the pager station.

596
00:37:35,460 --> 00:37:37,390
I'll give you the number
of the police station too.

597
00:37:37,690 --> 00:37:39,419
If you need help,
you can call the station

598
00:37:39,420 --> 00:37:40,800
and mention my name.

599
00:37:41,290 --> 00:37:42,070
Okay.

600
00:37:43,610 --> 00:37:44,329
Keep it safe.

601
00:37:44,330 --> 00:37:45,070
Okay.

602
00:37:48,940 --> 00:37:49,899
When I grow up,

603
00:37:49,900 --> 00:37:51,400
I want to be a good police officer

604
00:37:51,540 --> 00:37:52,760
like you

605
00:37:52,940 --> 00:37:54,249
and arrest all the bad guys.

606
00:37:54,250 --> 00:37:55,400
Me too.

607
00:37:56,500 --> 00:37:57,680
You too?

608
00:37:57,980 --> 00:37:59,880
Sweetie, working as a police officer
is dangerous.

609
00:38:00,260 --> 00:38:01,550
You have to consider it carefully.

610
00:38:02,460 --> 00:38:03,360
How

611
00:38:03,900 --> 00:38:04,859
about you learn the piano

612
00:38:04,860 --> 00:38:05,689
like your mom?

613
00:38:05,690 --> 00:38:07,200
Being a pianist is great too.

614
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:10,649
Since you like listening to Beyond,
you can form a band in the future.

615
00:38:10,650 --> 00:38:13,630
How can one person form a band?

616
00:38:13,860 --> 00:38:14,840
You have Tianming.

617
00:38:15,020 --> 00:38:16,550
Tianming likes Beyond too.

618
00:38:16,610 --> 00:38:18,070
You can form a band together.

619
00:38:19,060 --> 00:38:20,059
Beyond?

620
00:38:20,060 --> 00:38:21,240
What's that?

621
00:38:21,770 --> 00:38:23,110
I've never heard of it?

622
00:38:24,770 --> 00:38:27,030
- You haven't heard their songs yet, right?
- Not yet.

623
00:38:27,290 --> 00:38:28,680
This is good stuff.

624
00:38:28,900 --> 00:38:29,910
I'll let you hear it.

625
00:38:30,860 --> 00:38:32,360
You'll like it after you hear it.

626
00:38:32,380 --> 00:38:33,030
Here.

627
00:38:33,210 --> 00:38:34,379
I want to listen to it too.

628
00:38:34,380 --> 00:38:35,160
Okay.

629
00:38:35,290 --> 00:38:36,680
You'll get to listen to it too.

630
00:38:38,130 --> 00:38:38,595
Here you go.

631
00:38:38,596 --> 00:38:41,363
♪Every day I look at the sea♪

632
00:38:41,910 --> 00:38:44,757
♪I look at you every day♪

633
00:38:45,272 --> 00:38:46,964
♪I hope that you no longer have♪

634
00:38:46,965 --> 00:38:50,925
♪The fear of me leaving♪

635
00:38:51,910 --> 00:38:54,775
♪Even if I leave♪

636
00:38:55,239 --> 00:38:57,910
♪You'll still have me in your sky♪

637
00:38:58,555 --> 00:39:01,439
♪Do you know♪

638
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:05,162
♪Who is willing to return?♪

639
00:39:05,195 --> 00:39:11,162
♪Who will it be between us?♪

640
00:39:22,170 --> 00:39:23,070
It's all gone.

641
00:39:23,460 --> 00:39:24,200
That's all I have.

642
00:39:49,347 --> 00:39:51,560
(To Mai Zhihong)

643
00:40:00,500 --> 00:40:01,320
Miss.

644
00:40:01,940 --> 00:40:03,289
When I fed the dogs at the park,

645
00:40:03,290 --> 00:40:04,360
I saw this box.

646
00:40:09,220 --> 00:40:11,309
(Police Reinvestigate
King Shun Building Fire Incident)

647
00:40:11,310 --> 00:40:14,840
(Fire Not an Accident Cause of Fire is Suspicious)
They're finally willing to investigate it.

648
00:40:16,170 --> 00:40:17,710
